content.query:
SELECT
[unitIdName]
,[moveKind]
,[cheID]
,max([EcEventTime]) as time
,[typeDescription]
 FROM [dbo].[ecevents]
    WHERE Year = 2024 AND Month = 1 AND unitIdName = 'TCNU6890381'
    AND moveKind in ('LOAD' , 'DSCH') AND typeDescription in ('DSPT' , 'DROP', 'EARW','EASH') AND cheKind = 'SC'
    GROUP By unitIdName, moveKind, typeDescription, cheId
    ORDER BY time ASC
